summary:
As a math analyst in the casino game industry, I specialize in creating models of games to analyse statistics and provide data-driven insights. My strong background in mathematics, combined with my expertise in programming and data processing, allows me to deliver accurate and insightful analyses that drive business success.

I love the problem-solving nature of my role and take pride in writing code to implement and analyse game logic. In my free time, I also enjoy tutoring high school students in mathematics.

I am excited to see how the new AI revolution can increase the potential of data science and am eager to apply my skills and expertise to tackle complex challenges in this field. I stay up to date with the latest developments in data science through continuous learning and staying abreast of industry trends.

If you are interested in learning more about my skills and experience, please feel free to connect with me. I am always looking to network with like-minded professionals and explore new opportunities.
